# Ball

- _Ball(c, r)_

A `Type` representing a ball,
also called a solid sphere,
centered at point _c_ with radius _r_.

```
>>> let b = Ball([0 0 0], 1);
>>> (
>>> 	b.center,
>>> 	b.radius,
>>> 	b.volume
>>> )
([0 0 0], 1, 4/3.pi)
```

